 "body": "<p>S687-S689 Income Tax (Trading and Other Income) Act 2005, S979-S981 Corporation Tax Act 2009</p>\n\n<p>This section looks at the taxation of income not otherwise charged to Income Tax or Corporation Tax. Such income is subject to a stand-alone charge (the sweep-up charge) to Income Tax or Corporation Tax under the category of ‘miscellaneous income’.</p>\n\n<p>This guidance does not cover other stand-alone charges within the miscellaneous income category.</p>\n\n<p>This section contains the following guidance:</p>\n",
